snippet.title: Stormy Parliament Session Expected Today, PM Modi Likely to be Present during Debate

localized.description:
Winter Session of Parliament 2016: Stormy Parliament session expected today. PM Modi likely to be present during debate. Opposition parties are attacking PM Modi for demonetising Rs 500 and Rs 1000 notes without any preparation.
